---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Careers — Rentar Environmental Solutions | Rentar"
  description="Join Rentar Environmental Solutions. Explore career opportunities in engineering, sales, operations, and technology at the forefront of fuel efficiency innovation."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:35vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Join Us</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">Careers</h1>
      <p>Help us reduce global fuel consumption. We're building the team that will deploy fuel catalyst technology at scale across the world's highest-fuel-consuming industries.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="section-label">Work at Rentar</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Build the future of fuel efficiency</h2>
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>Rentar Environmental Solutions is growing. We're looking for exceptional people who want to work at the intersection of mechanical engineering, data science, telemetry, and industrial decarbonization.</p>
        <p>We don't have open positions listed online at this time, but we're always interested in hearing from talented engineers, sales professionals, and operations specialists who share our mission.</p>
        <p>To inquire about opportunities, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com" style="color:var(--orange);">info@rentar.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
